From the console sidebar, navigate to the Node groups page. Expand PE Infrastructure (click +) and then click PE Master.

Add the repository class for the agent node OS that you want to support.

On the Classes tab, in the Add new class field, enter pe_repo.
From the list of classes, select the pe_repo::platform::ubuntu_2004_amd64 repo class.
Click Add class.

puppet agent -t ## on the master node ...

